column6: Parent (If this element is for example a bigger version of another, the other ones ID(decimal) goes here. "No" if this element is it's own.)
column7: Properties (Comma seperated list. None=Element does not have properties. Inherit=Same properties as Base Id)
column8: Name Combobulator (2=In-game selectable, 1=shows up, but not selectable, 0=displays raw)

column9: A downwards column of 16 Environment. Gets saved as Environment. No longer accessable in the game.
The round one used by golf mode. Actually called "Package" in the name combobulator (a different name is used here to have unique names for everything for better API).
